responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "D493823C4283CB24FEC8AA87E872E38B", "In a tiny realm far across the voided sea existed an apocalyptic world torn asunder by three. Tauros was the world and Tauroxians were they, once a great realm of no empires they say. But tyrants did rise when greed for gold grew, powerful warlords wished all coofers for the few. Great and long wars raged over the land toppling the grandeur all Tauroxians once had.")
